FRONTEND
* upload board
* start game
* creates room (with random id)
* generates qr code (because room id is probably insane)
* opens new tab (/board)

BACKEND
* gets new connection from me (with board and auth token)
* inits new room with board
* players connect with names
* host can start
* host can edit points
* players can hit buzzers

new connections
* players connect from buzzer site, added to array of player connections
* new authed connections added to array of host connections